  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add 1 small onion, finely chopped, and cook until translucent.",
    "Add 1 small bell pepper, finely chopped, and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add 1 pound of rest-meat, breaking it up with a spoon as it cooks.",
    "Add 2 cloves of garlic, minced, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add 1 teaspoon of paprika, 1 teaspoon of cumin, and 1/2 teaspoon of cayenne pepper.",
    "Stir in 1 cup of crushed digestive biscuits.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
